= Tor Browser =
Tor Browser's built-in update check mechanism also works in {{project name}}, so use it whenever updates become available. <ref>
The only exception is Tor Browser running in a DisposableVM in [[Qubes|{{q_project_name}}]], since the update will not persist.
</ref>

For additional information about Tor Browser updates see [[Tor_Browser#Update_Tor_Browser|Tor Browser]]. Additionally, consider subscribing to https://blog.torproject.org for developments from The Tor Project.

